snippet.title: Amber heard status
snippet.description:
Amber Laura Heard is an American film and television actress. After a series of small roles in film and television, Heard had her first starring role in the horror film All the Boys Love Mandy Lane.Born: 22 April 1986 (age 35 years), Austin, Texas, United States
TV shows: The Stand, Criminal Minds, The Playboy Club, The O.C., Overhaulin', Hidden Palm #Amber @mohit chaudhari  Heard#emmawatson#jenniferlawrence#alexandara daddarrio#selenagomez
